==Geographic distribution==
Ili Turki is in China's [[Ili Kazakh Autonomous Prefecture]] along the [[Ili River]] and its tributaries and in [[Yining City|Yining]].  There may be some speakers in [[Kazakhstan]].  Ili Turki has no official status in either country.

