'''Jan Awei''' is a moribund [[Jukunoid language]] of [[Nigeria]]. It had around 12 speakers in 1997 and was spoken in an area West of the Muri Mountains in the far South of [[Gombe State]], however the precise location is unknown.<ref name=":0" />
