'''Jo Baka''' is an [[Internet meme]] that became popular in [[Gujarat]], [[India]].<ref name="Guardian article">{{cite news|title=Jo Baka: the Gujarati internet meme that went viral|url=https://www.theguardian.com/cities/2014/oct/16/jo-baka-viral-meme-gujarati-india-facebook-whatsapp|accessdate=24 February 2015|publisher=The Guardian|date=16 Oct 2014}}</ref> It [[translation|translates]] as "look dear", and it is used as a [[prefix]] for various funny [[one-line joke|one-liners]] and public messages.
A [[Gujarati people|Gujarati]] rapper also composed a song around this meme.(E.X Jo baka taklif to rehvani <ref>{{cite news|title=Gujarati rapper pens song on 'Jo Baka' meme|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/vadodara/Gujarati-rapper-pens-song-on-Jo-Baka-meme/articleshow/44797591.cms|agency=Times News Service|publisher=Bennet and Coleman|date=2014-10-13}}</ref>

